'''吠獸'''（{{lang-en|Questing Beast}}、{{lang-cy|Cwestiynu Bwystfil}}、或{{lang-en|Barking Beast}}、古法語: Beste Glatissant）是[[亞瑟王傳說|亞瑟王傳說]]中登場的架空怪物，因其叫聲宛如30對[[獵犬|獵犬]]一起吠叫而得名<ref>OED. quest "2 Of hunting dogs: To break out into a peculiar bark at the sight of game; to give tongue; to bark or yelp. ''Obs. exc. dial.''"</ref>。為了狩獵此獸，[[珀西瓦里|波西瓦]]騎士等人展開冒險。

== 概要 ==
吠獸是擁有[[蛇|蛇]]的頭和尾、豹的身體、[[獅|獅]]尾、[[鹿|鹿]]足的異形生物。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uiweb.uidaho.edu/student_orgs/arthurian_legend/quests/monsters/abeasts.html |title=Arthurian Legend - Monsters |publisher=Uiweb.uidaho.edu |accessdate=2014-06-14 |url-status= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109203139/http://www.uiweb.uidaho.edu/student_orgs/arthurian_legend/quests/monsters/abeasts.html |archivedate=2013-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最初的文献紀錄是13世紀和之後的聖杯傳說，最後在『[[亞瑟之死|亞瑟之死]]』中登場。

